#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:338
msgid ""
"LMCache integrates with TensorRT-LLM via TRT-LLM's **KV Cache Connector**"
" API and supports two deployment modes:"
msgstr ""
"LMCache 通过 TRT-LLM 的 **KV Cache Connector** API 与 TensorRT-LLM "
"集成，并支持两种部署模式："

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:341
msgid ""
"**In-process mode** (``connector: lmcache``) -- LMCache runs as a "
"singleton inside the TRT-LLM process. Simplest setup; no extra service to"
" manage."
msgstr ""
"**进程内模式** (``connector: lmcache``) -- LMCache 作为单例在 TRT-LLM "
"进程内运行。最简单的设置；无需管理额外的服务。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:344
msgid ""
"**MP mode** (``connector: lmcache-mp``) -- LMCache runs as a standalone "
"server. Multiple TRT-LLM workers on the same node can share the cache, "
"and the cache survives a TRT-LLM crash."
msgstr ""
"**MP 模式** (``connector: lmcache-mp``) -- LMCache 作为独立服务器运行。多个 TRT-LLM "
"工作进程可以共享缓存，并且缓存在 TRT-LLM 崩溃后仍然存在。"

