#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:452
msgid ""
"**CPU-only (no GPU)** -- the server runs with a ``StubCPUDevice`` and "
"shares KV tensors with vLLM over POSIX shared memory. Start ``lmcache "
"server`` normally, then set ``lmcache.mp.mp_transfer_mode=engine_driven``"
" on the vLLM side to enable the zero-copy SHM path."
msgstr "**仅 CPU（无 GPU）** -- 服务器使用 ``StubCPUDevice`` 运行，并通过 POSIX 共享内存与 vLLM 共享 KV 张量。正常启动 ``lmcache server``，然后在 vLLM 端设置 ``lmcache.mp.mp_transfer_mode=engine_driven`` 以启用零拷贝 SHM 路径。"

